summary: An Ordinance appropriating One Hundred Fifty ($150.00) Dollars, or so much thereof as may be necessary, from the General Fund of The City of Seattle to Local Improvement Fund Condemnation Award District No. 3009, to meet a deficit in said Local Improvement Fund Condemnation Award District No. 3009 created by the reduction by the court of a certain assessment in the assessment roll of Empire Way Condemnation and judgment confirming the same, under Ordinance No. 30673, Cause No. 98096 of the Superior Court of the State of Washington for King County.
